4. ________________________ - Why: ________________________________________
5. ________________________ - Why: ________________________________________

REFLECTION QUESTIONS:
1. Which values surprised you to see on your list?
2. Are there any values you thought would be important but didn't make your top 5?
3. How might unclear values contribute to dating uncertainty?
4. How can knowing your top values help you in ambiguous dating situations?

APPLICATION:
Before pursuing romantic interest, check in: Does this potential connection align with my top 5 values?